Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:25.60,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Musí tam byť niečo mimo mňa.
Dialogue: 4,0:01:37.73,0:01:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buď opatrný, Jin-tan!
Dialogue: 4,0:01:42.12,0:01:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yadomi?
Dialogue: 4,0:01:43.06,0:01:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Som v poriadku!
Dialogue: 4,0:01:50.75,0:01:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 4,0:01:52.97,0:01:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tie biele šaty...
Dialogue: 4,0:01:56.85,0:01:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sú podobné, aké nosila Menma.
Dialogue: 4,0:02:00.76,0:02:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si sa tak obliekol?
Dialogue: 4,0:02:06.34,0:02:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 4,0:02:10.89,0:02:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzerám,{\i1} že som{\i0\fscx140} {\r}v poriadku?
Dialogue: 4,0:02:19.84,0:02:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No tak, pozeraj sa dobre!
Dialogue: 4,0:02:22.07,0:02:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Yukiatsu!
Dialogue: 4,0:02:25.57,0:02:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, nechaj ich na pokoji.
Dialogue: 4,0:02:28.53,0:02:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 4,0:02:29.72,0:02:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je jeho príležitosť.
Dialogue: 4,0:02:31.14,0:02:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keby sa nepošmykol, tak možno nikdy...
Dialogue: 4,0:02:35.19,0:02:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuruko...
Dialogue: 4,0:02:40.64,0:02:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre?
Dialogue: 4,0:02:42.20,0:02:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzerám snáď ako Menma?
Dialogue: 4,0:02:44.13,0:02:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vidíš ma ako Menmu, nie?
Dialogue: 4,0:02:47.41,0:02:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzerám ako Menma?
Dialogue: 4,0:02:49.50,0:02:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukia—
Dialogue: 4,0:02:50.13,0:02:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzerám rovnako ako ona?
Dialogue: 4,0:02:52.84,0:02:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola to moja vina!
Dialogue: 4,0:02:55.10,0:02:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola to moja vina, že v ten deň Menma zomrela.
Dialogue: 4,0:02:59.77,0:03:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to hovoríš?
Dialogue: 4,0:03:01.17,0:03:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To nebola tvoja vina!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:02.90,0:03:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola to moja vina—
Dialogue: 4,0:03:03.48,0:03:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedal som, že to bola moja vina!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:05.89,0:03:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma by nezomrela, keby som jej to nepovedal.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:10.39,0:03:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som zavinil smrť Menmy.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:16.99,0:03:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som ten, kto chcel vidieť Menmu.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:20.27,0:03:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keď je duch alebo prekliatie, aby ma...
Dialogue: 4,0:03:22.99,0:03:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som ten, kto ju chcel vidieť ako prvý!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:30.22,0:03:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale Menma sa neobjavila.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:35.20,0:03:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie predo mnou.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:38.30,0:03:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu...
Dialogue: 4,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je dôvod, prečo tu už Menma nie je.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ona už nie je nikde!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale ja som tu.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:57.97,0:04:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma hovorí, že je tu.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:03.24,0:04:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Už zase?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:07.84,0:04:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma hovorí, "ďakujem za sponku do vlasov".
Dialogue: 4,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ona hovorí, "Ospravedlňujem sa".
Dialogue: 4,0:04:19.69,0:04:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, ja naozaj tomu nerozumiem, ale...
Dialogue: 4,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:36.12,0:04:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Si šťastná?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:39.96,0:04:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hej!
Dialogue: 4,0:04:41.47,0:04:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mali by sme ho nechať ísť?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:46.79,0:04:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To svrbí.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:50.79,0:04:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja už idem...
Dialogue: 4,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vedela si to o ňom?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:58.35,0:05:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol to len taký pocit.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:01.35,0:05:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Po škole bol so mnou dosť často.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:06.88,0:05:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Predstieral, že dáva darčeky svojej priateľke, ktorú som nikdy nevidela.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:12.19,0:05:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raz kúpil dievčenské biele šaty a modrú stužku.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:19.99,0:05:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Si si istá, že je v poriadku?
Dialogue: 4,0:05:22.33,0:05:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vypustiť zo seba všetku zlosť je najúčinnejšie.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:25.84,0:05:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keď je zvnútra skazený.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:30.05,0:05:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak ho nemusíš za to odsudzovať.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:36.03,0:05:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem ti.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:44.96,0:05:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ďakujem ti za sponku do vlasov".
Dialogue: 4,0:05:47.89,0:05:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ospravedlňujem sa".
Dialogue: 4,0:05:59.19,0:06:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma...
Dialogue: 4,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj, Jin-tan!
Dialogue: 4,0:06:04.41,0:06:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan!
Dialogue: 4,0:06:05.66,0:06:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj!
Dialogue: 4,0:06:07.12,0:06:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj, Menma!
Dialogue: 4,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo? Ja nemôžem čakať!
Dialogue: 4,0:06:10.34,0:06:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan je—
Dialogue: 4,0:06:10.94,0:06:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Len nech ten idiot uteká!
Dialogue: 4,0:06:18.53,0:06:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma, ty nie si škaredá.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma...
Dialogue: 4,0:06:23.57,0:06:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu máš...
Dialogue: 4,0:06:26.30,0:06:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslel som, že by ti to pasovalo k šatám.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:30.36,0:06:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milujem ťa, Menma!
Dialogue: 4,0:06:43.01,0:06:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč!
Dialogue: 4,0:06:44.33,0:06:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan už odišiel!
Dialogue: 4,0:06:47.24,0:06:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma musí ísť za ním.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:50.80,0:06:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Porozprávame sa neskôr!
Dialogue: 4,0:06:53.31,0:06:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma...
Dialogue: 4,0:07:34.41,0:07:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím, že to nepasuje k mojim okuliarom.
Dialogue: 4,0:07:41.85,0:07:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A teraz nič nevidím.
Dialogue: 4,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Men—
Dialogue: 4,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma...
Dialogue: 4,0:08:00.78,0:08:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... chceš niečo jesť?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:04.39,0:08:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 4,0:08:06.26,0:08:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken-chan rámen!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:07.99,0:08:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemáme to...
Dialogue: 4,0:08:10.12,0:08:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V skutočnosti som to v poslednej dobe ani v obchodoch nevidel.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:13.72,0:08:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak, čo si dám?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:15.92,0:08:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 4,0:08:18.61,0:08:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pôjdem niečo kúpiť.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:20.40,0:08:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neobťažuj sa, zjem niečo, čo tu máme.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:25.54,0:08:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:27.33,0:08:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma zomrela.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:29.89,0:08:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale ona je tu.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:32.21,0:08:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V mojom dome, a nie v dome Yukiatsa.
