Dialogue: 4,0:08:36.06,0:08:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je mi jedno, či je duch alebo halucinácia.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To som si myslel.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:41.79,0:08:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 4,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestal som o tom premýšľať.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:47.79,0:08:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola to zábava s každým.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:50.99,0:08:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola to zábava s Jin-tan.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:54.04,0:08:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je dôvod, prečo časť mňa cítila, aby som naozaj nad tým nepremýšľala.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:01.87,0:09:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo je Menma tu?
Dialogue: 4,0:09:07.18,0:09:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Si príliš populárna.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 4,0:09:35.40,0:09:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemali tam Ken-chan rámen, tak som doniesol toto.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:38.31,0:09:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto všetko namiesto toho?
Dialogue: 4,0:09:41.80,0:09:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poď, sadni si a...
Dialogue: 4,0:09:50.35,0:09:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan, chcem ti niečo povedať.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Niečo povedať?
Dialogue: 4,0:09:55.79,0:09:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To môže počkať, Garigari-kun bude teplý, ak...
Dialogue: 4,0:09:58.45,0:10:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem, aby si splnil moje prianie.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to teraz {\i1}hovoríš{\i0\fscx30} {\r}?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:05.78,0:10:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty chceš, aby som ti splnil tvoje prianie.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:08.23,0:10:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robím, čo môžem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:12.64,0:10:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som nebol stále deprimovaný, kvôli Yukiatsu, ale...
Dialogue: 4,0:10:19.17,0:10:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... snažím sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:25.54,0:10:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som dosť zaneprázdnený človek!
Dialogue: 4,0:10:28.59,0:10:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem sa celý čas starať o teba.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:32.22,0:10:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan...
Dialogue: 4,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Som doma!
Dialogue: 4,0:10:35.91,0:10:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Človeče, som unavený.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:38.07,0:10:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, máme večierok alebo niečo také?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:40.71,0:10:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Garigari-kun!
Dialogue: 4,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aké roztomilé!
Dialogue: 4,0:10:43.60,0:10:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Môžem si to zobrať?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:47.46,0:10:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To nie je roztomilé...
Dialogue: 4,0:10:49.99,0:10:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to sakra?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:53.29,0:10:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo mám robiť?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:55.17,0:10:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako som zaneprázdnený?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:57.38,0:11:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jem, surfujem na internete, spím, hrám sa, spím, jem...
Dialogue: 4,0:11:04.54,0:11:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stále sa to opakuje.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:06.88,0:11:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 4,0:11:12.74,0:11:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale... !
