Dialogue: 4,0:15:23.35,0:15:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale, nehovoril si...
Dialogue: 4,0:15:24.70,0:15:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo sa chceš vrátiť?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:27.35,0:15:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viem, že máš čierne nohavičky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj...
Dialogue: 4,0:15:33.07,0:15:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie! Prestaň! Nedotýkaj sa ma!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:36.03,0:15:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, áno.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:37.29,0:15:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nehovor áno, áno!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:39.92,0:15:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pusti ma!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:41.54,0:15:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do čerta s tebou!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:42.41,0:15:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pusti ma!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:45.07,0:15:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Anjou?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:48.99,0:15:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idem sa zabávať s Yadomi.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:52.54,0:15:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chceš sa k nám pridať?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:53.71,0:15:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto sakra si?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:55.71,0:15:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, všetci tadiaľ!
Dialogue: 4,0:16:00.63,0:16:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je smiešne...
Dialogue: 4,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zachránil som dievča, ktoré chcel znásilniť muž...
Dialogue: 4,0:16:19.74,0:16:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To musí byť viac stereotypných veci v mojom živote.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:23.58,0:16:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To ma zachránilo?
Dialogue: 4,0:16:25.69,0:16:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemal si mu skôr dať päsťou a zobrať ma preč?
Dialogue: 4,0:16:28.47,0:16:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som šikovný a pekný, ale nie som veľmi silný.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to má byť... ?
Dialogue: 4,0:16:34.13,0:16:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okrem toho...
Dialogue: 4,0:16:36.21,0:16:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je bolestivé pozerať sa na teba.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:38.87,0:16:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty máš čo rozprávať.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:40.80,0:16:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty transvestita.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:44.60,0:16:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:46.24,0:16:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím, že je lepšie, keď ma voláš takto.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:50.29,0:16:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty si panna?
Dialogue: 4,0:16:53.76,0:16:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Č-Č-Č-Čo, máš s tým nejaký problém?
Dialogue: 4,0:16:59.40,0:17:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chceš to skúsiť so mnou?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:05.69,0:17:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemiluješ náhodou Menmu?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:08.34,0:17:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je pravda.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:10.54,0:17:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:12.29,0:17:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja nemôžem!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:13.52,0:17:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja jednoducho nemôžem.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:15.56,0:17:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:16.51,0:17:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to kvôli Yadomimu?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:18.73,0:17:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je na ňom také dobré?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:20.41,0:17:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo myslíš tým, čo je na ňom dobré?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:22.14,0:17:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevymýšľaj si!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:23.53,0:17:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som nikdy nepovedala, že ho milujem...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:25.08,0:17:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On bol vodcom všetkých.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:26.76,0:17:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On bol šikovný a silný.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:29.71,0:17:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale to všetko je už minulosť.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:31.46,0:17:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No áno, ale...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:33.92,0:17:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On vie byť až prekvapivo milý.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:36.34,0:17:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On vyzerá trochu ako Yama-chan z {\i1}Hej! Povedz! Skoč!{\i0\fscx140} {\r}Keď si opravuje vlasy—
Dialogue: 4,0:17:42.05,0:17:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozumiem.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja neviem, či ho milujem.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:52.54,0:17:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja jednoducho nemôžem... Yadomiho dostať zo svojej mysle.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:56.94,0:17:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dostať z mysle?
Dialogue: 4,0:18:01.02,0:18:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Potom, čo Menma a jeho mama zomrela, je veľmi ťažké sa rozprávať s Yadomim.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:09.39,0:18:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola som šťastná, že sme sa dostali do rovnakej triedy.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:14.05,0:18:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale Yadomi nemôže zabudnúť na Menmu.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:19.05,0:18:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ty nemôžeš zabudnúť na Yadomiho, ktorý nemôže zabudnúť na Menmu.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:25.39,0:18:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Predtým...
Dialogue: 4,0:18:27.34,0:18:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepovedal si náhodou Yadomiho meno, Yukiatsu?
Dialogue: 4,0:18:31.34,0:18:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedal si, že sa s ním ideš zabávať.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:40.60,0:18:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Expresný vlak o chvíľu prejde.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:42.26,0:18:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím počkajte.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:46.01,0:18:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obaja sme sa stratili.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V poriadku.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:07.16,0:19:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ťuk, ťuk, ťuk...
Dialogue: 4,0:19:10.70,0:19:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ting!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vynikajúce!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:20.23,0:19:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si prišiel na večeru ku mne domov?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:23.49,0:19:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doniesol som horskú zeleninu.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:26.69,0:19:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tá tempura stojí za to!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:29.43,0:19:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poppo je pri jedle naozaj šťastný!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:32.44,0:19:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jedlo máš na nose.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dobre, Menma je tu?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, Menma je tu!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:40.77,0:19:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma, daj si tiež nejakú tempuru!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:44.72,0:19:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty naozaj veríš v Menmu?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovoril som to už minule!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:51.59,0:19:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 4,0:19:54.45,0:19:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslel som na to znova.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:57.87,0:20:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja naozaj neviem, ale nemyslím si, že sú okolo Menmy dobré veci.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Možno, že nemôže ísť do neba.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:07.94,0:20:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže preto je tu ona?
Dialogue: 4,0:20:10.09,0:20:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ísť... do neba...
Dialogue: 4,0:20:14.64,0:20:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja to neviem určite...
Dialogue: 4,0:20:17.75,0:20:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 4,0:20:18.61,0:20:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan?
Dialogue: 4,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma—
Dialogue: 4,0:20:21.02,0:20:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma je práve tu?
Dialogue: 4,0:20:22.64,0:20:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 4,0:20:24.24,0:20:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:25.95,0:20:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, počkaj...
Dialogue: 4,0:20:26.90,0:20:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahoj, Menma!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:28.49,0:20:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Môžeš mi dať nejaké znamenie?
Dialogue: 4,0:20:32.03,0:20:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urobím ťuk, ťuk, ting vec.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:35.48,0:20:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Máš prianie, však?
Dialogue: 4,0:20:37.79,0:20:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Na mňa sa môžeš tiež spoľahnúť.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:40.91,0:20:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem ti pomôcť, aby si išla do neba.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:44.13,0:20:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Hisakawa...
Dialogue: 4,0:20:45.84,0:20:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No tak, Menma.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:47.40,0:20:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, povedz mi to.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:49.22,0:20:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Objav sa aj mne, nie len Jin-tanovi!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie?
Dialogue: 4,0:20:56.09,0:20:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:56.68,0:20:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:00.58,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)\pos(26,56)\fs38\an7\be6}Naše leto sa skončilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:00.58,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)\pos(26,16)\an7\fs38\be6}Kimi to natsu no owari
Dialogue: 4,0:20:59.75,0:21:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma chce tiež hovoriť s ostatnými.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:05.31,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,180)\pos(26,56)\fs38\an7\be6}Nezabudnem na veľké nádeje a sny o budúcnosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:05.31,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,180)\pos(26,16)\an7\fs38\be6}Shourai no yume ooki na kibou wasurenai
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.31,0:21:12.12,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\pos(26,56)\fs38\an7\be6}Verím, že sa zase stretneme o desať rokov v auguste ako teraz.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.31,0:21:12.12,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\pos(26,16)\an7\fs38\be6}Juunengo no hachigatsu mata deaeru no wo shinjite
Dialogue: 4,0:21:07.41,0:21:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale, ja neviem ako.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:08.15,0:21:09.62,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Menma.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:09.62,0:21:12.12,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,Budeme premýšľať všetci spoločne.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:10.28,0:21:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moje prianie je cesta do neba...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.44,0:21:20.37,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,1080)\pos(26,56)\fs38\an7\be6}Ďakujem ti za spomienky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.44,0:21:20.37,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,1080)\pos(26,16)\an7\fs38\be6}Saikou no omoide wo
Dialogue: 4,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja nič neviem!
Dialogue: 4,0:21:16.69,0:21:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No tak, prečo nie?
Dialogue: 4,0:21:18.15,0:21:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, budeme všetci spoločne premýšľať!
Dialogue: 4,0:21:20.27,0:21:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja neviem...
Dialogue: 4,0:21:22.50,0:21:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma, potom...
Dialogue: 4,0:21:23.47,0:21:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poppo!
Dialogue: 4,0:21:30.42,0:21:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Môžeš s tým už prestať?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:36.07,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\pos(26,56)\fs38\an7\be6}Náhodou sme sa stretli v tomto momente.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:36.07,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\pos(26,16)\an7\fs38\be6}Deai wa futto shita shunkan
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:39.56,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\pos(26,56)\fs38\an7\be6}Na križovatke na mojej ceste domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:39.56,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\pos(26,16)\an7\fs38\be6}Kaerimichi no kousaten de
Dialogue: 4,0:21:36.46,0:21:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:38.24,0:21:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň už s tým.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:45.46,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\pos(26,56)\fs38\an7\be6}Povedal si mi: "Poďme domov spolu".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:45.46,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\pos(26,16)\an7\fs38\be6}Koe wo kakete kureta ne "issho ni kaerou"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:51.99,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)\pos(26,56)\fs38\an7\be6}Oh, ohňostroj krásne rozkvitol na nočnej oblohe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:51.99,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)\pos(26,16)\an7\fs38\be6}Ah hanabi ga yozora kirei ni saite
Dialogue: 4,0:21:47.21,0:21:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja to neviem...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:53.99,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,180)\pos(26,56)\fs38\an7\be6}Napriek tomu to bolo trochu smutné.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:53.99,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,180)\pos(26,16)\an7\fs38\be6}Chotto setsunaku
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:22:00.73,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\pos(26,56)\fs38\an7\be6}Oh, vietor a čas plynie spolu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:22:00.73,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\pos(26,16)\an7\fs38\be6}Ah kaze ga jikan to tomo ni nagareru
Dialogue: 4,0:21:56.89,0:21:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja to neviem!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:04.63,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Ureshikutte tanoshikutte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:04.63,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Bola som tak šťastná a všetko bolo také zábavné.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:08.21,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Zažili sme spolu veľa dobrodružstiev.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:08.21,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Bouken mo iroiro shita ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.21,0:22:15.01,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Vo vnútri v našej tajnej skrýši.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.21,0:22:15.01,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Futari no himitsu no kichi no naka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:17.54,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)\be6}Naše leto sa skončilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:17.54,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)\be6}Kimi to natsu no owari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.54,0:22:22.55,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,180)\be6}Nezabudnem na veľké nádeje a sny o budúcnosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.54,0:22:22.55,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,180)\be6}Shourai no yume ooki na kibou wasurenai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:29.63,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Verím, že sa zase stretneme o desať rokov v auguste ako teraz.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:29.63,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Juunengo no hachigatsu mata deaeru no wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.63,0:22:33.66,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)\be6}Viem, že si mi povedal "ďakujem"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.63,0:22:33.66,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)\be6}Kimi ga saigo made kokoro kara "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:36.68,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,180)\be6}S tvojím srdcom až do samého konca.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:36.68,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,180)\be6}Sakendeita koto shitteita yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:43.95,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Bolo to tak veľmi ťažké udržať slzy a rozlúčiť sa s úsmevom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:43.95,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Namida wo koraete egao de sayounara setsunai yo ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.95,0:22:52.51,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,1080)\be6}Ďakujem ti za spomienky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.95,0:22:52.51,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,1080)\be6}Saikou no omoide wo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.44,0:22:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do jamy! Do jamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.81,0:23:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
